title: "Black Hole Simulation Lab (BlackHoleDS / OPPENGROK)"
message: >-
  If you use or refer to this software, please cite it as below.
  The human author and Human-in-the-Loop is Alexander Donahue; the
  work was produced with substantial AI assistance under his direction
  and review (see AUTHORS and docs/log/DECISIONS.md, ADR-0012).
type: software
authors:
